PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the PIAPOT BAND, of some 1320 hectares of land situated in the Rural Municipality of Cuper No. 218, near Markinch, Saskatchewan, together with the mines and minerals existing within, upon or under a road allowance comprising some 0.417 hectares, all as additions to Piapot First Nation Indian Reserve No. 75T.
